name: Dominic Ligammari
text: Probably the best Pizza Hut I've been too, and they have a lunch buffet every day for under $9! The only issue I could find with the buffet was they didn't have any icing out for the cinnamon sticks. Otherwise, the food was great and they kept bringing out more pizza the whole time. Would recommend this place for lunch absolutely.

name: Joe Ibbetson
text: My wife and I ordered a super supreme pan pizza take out on 7/28/17.  Quite frankly it was the best we've ever had! Perfect  crispy crust with "picture perfect" toppings. Seriously, I should have taken a picture and posted it, it was that …More

name: Josh Brent
text: Possibly the best pizza I've had in my life!  I was stunned.  Can't wait to try again in a few weeks to see  if they can repeat.  We had carry-out, done just as I walked in. Friendly service too.
